Questions

  • Is at least one of the predictors useful in predicting the response? F-statistic.

  • Do all the predictors help to explain Y, or is it a subset of predictors that help to explain Y? Compare models with different subsets. Metric include AIC, BIC, adjusted R2 and Mallowâs \[C_{p}\].

  • How well does the model fit the data? RSE and R2 (training data)

  • Given a set of predictor values, what response value should we predict? And, how accurate is our prediction? RSE and R2 (test data)
